snippet.title: Kinect Nat Geo TV trailer
snippet.description: "Kinect Nat Geo TV" blends world-renowned Nat Geo WILD TV programs with intuitive Kinect for Xbox 360 technology, transporting children and their families to animal habitats around the world to inspire a sense of wonder and excitement about nature. Through the magic of "reach in and explore" interactivity on Kinect, kids do more than just watch television — they will engage, play and learn using their full bodies, gestures and voices.
